Finding 8: Input Handling in Search Functionality
Application: Juice Shop
Severity: Low
OWASP Category: Injection
Endpoint:
/rest/products/search?q=

Description:
User input is passed directly into search queries without strong validation.

Impact:
•	Potential injection attack surface 
•	Unpredictable application behavior
Solution:
•	Validate input length and format 
•	Sanitize user input 
•	Use safe query handling 

