Finding 9: Stored Input Handling in Reviews

Application: Juice Shop
Severity: Medium
OWASP Category: Injection
Endpoint:
/rest/products/reviews

Description:
User-submitted reviews are stored and rendered dynamically. Improper handling could allow client-side injection if not encoded.

Impact:
•	Persistent user-controlled content 
•	Potential client-side attacks 
Solution:
•	Encode output before rendering 
•	Validate input 
•	Apply CSP 

